     1	"""Shared fixtures for the ``Store`` conformance suite.
     2	
     3	Every test that takes ``make_store`` runs against the full set of
     4	reference backends via pytest parametrization. ``memory`` and
     5	``sqlite`` always run; ``postgres`` runs when the
